     ```
     - All bookings with SocialPreference.NONE:
     ```java
     List<BookingRequest> bookings = selected.stream()
             .map(id -> new BookingRequest(id, SocialPreference.NONE, rng.nextBoolean(), false))
             .collect(Collectors.toList());
     ```
     - Anonymous OrgChartService:
     ```java
     OrgChartService orgChartService = new OrgChartService() {
         @Override public Map<String, Employee> getEmployees() { return employees; }
         @Override public Map<String, OrgNode> getOrgNodes() { return orgNodes; }
     };
     ```
     - Output: flat table sorted alphabetically by desk name, columns: Desk | Neighborhood | Employee | Team (depth-4 first name) | WIN
     - QAP metrics: siblings (tree dist=1), same sub-org (dist 2-5), cross-team (dist 6+), clustering ratio
     - Last observed results: 170 sampled, ~350ms, clustering ratio ~11-12x, siblings avg ~172-227 units, cross-team ~2136 units

   - **`frontend/src/api/stubs.ts`** (READ, needs to be UPDATED)
